= The strategy congress of 1971

A new sexenio, and the oldest question, formally on the table: which road? The delegates know the price list by heart — the political road builds slowly and legally toward doors that may be painted on walls; the armed road answers the state in its own grammar and forfeits every legal instrument while it runs.

Echeverría offers apertura with one hand; Guerrero bleeds under the other. The hall is full of people who buried friends in October and buried more in the winters since.

- @via_politica: The political road: organization, elections where they exist, the long accumulation.
- @via_armada: The armed road: build the rural and urban structures. The Movement goes to war.

@via_politica
on-arrival: via = "politica"; unity += 2

The resolution passes; the tools remain the press, the assembly, the casilla. Whatever the sierra decides, it will decide without your signature.

@via_armada
choose-if: guerrilla_meter >= 8 or postura_guerrilla >= 2
unavailable-subtitle: A war needs willing soldiers: without a hot temptation among the youth or prior channels, the resolution would empty the hall.
