The resolution is read once, burned, and never minuted. Structures split: a legal face that knows nothing, and columns that know everything. The Sierra tab opens on your desk — and somewhere in the Defensa Nacional building, a colonel pins a new map to a corkboard. Both maps will now be maintained in parallel, at compounding cost.
